<div class='clearfix'>

    <div class='col col-12 py4 border-first-panel relative bc-white bg-mandarine min-panel-height' style='z-index:1'>
      <div class='clearfix py4 px2 flex items-center mx-auto'>
        <div class='col col-12 py4 flex flex-column center'>
          <div class='max-width-3 mx-auto'>
            <p class='mx-auto h1 my0 sofiabold pb1 dgray'>Connect to your community through<span class='accent-color'> volunteering.</span></p>
            <p class='mx-auto h5 MuseoSans300 px4 py3 dgray'>
              Volunteer with local, credible community organization (currently beta testing in NYC).
            </p>
          </div>

          <%= render "layouts/public/partials/category_cards", locals: @categories, mode: "filter" %>

          <div id='collapse-sub-header'></div>
          <% content_for :sub_header do %>
            <%= render "layouts/public/partials/activations_sub_header", locals: @categories %>
          <% end %>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='before-faq-panel col col-12 py4 my4 bg-mandarine min-panel-height'>
      <div class='clearfix flex items-center flex-wrap justify-center'>
        <% @activations.each do |activation| %>
          <%= render "layouts/public/partials/activation_card", activation: activation %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='faq-panel col col-12 pb4 min-panel-height'>
      <div class='clearfix pb4 px2 mx-auto max-width-4'>
        <div class='double-border-box-faq biggest-box index-page-box p1'>
          <p class='box-inner-text sofiabold h4 dgray'>A platform for activism</p>
          <p class='box-inner-text sofiabold h2 accent-color'><%= Rails.application.secrets.name %> is about getting involved in your community one day, and one cause at a time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class='faq-container'>
          <div class='faq-text-box'>
            <p class='sub-heading sofiabold dgray'>The fine print</p>
            <p class='faq-subheading sofiabold dgray h4'>How we operate</p>
            <p class='faq-text h5'>
              <%= Rails.application.secrets.name %> is a non-profit federal tax-exempt organization under section 501(c)(3) of the Internal Revenue Code, EIN 81-4924613, so all of your donations are tax deductible.
            </p>
            <p class='faq-text h5'>
              While volunteering doesn’t cost any money, some activations might require tools and supplies, most of which <%= Rails.application.secrets.name %> aims to provide. Interested in donating supplies? Email us at <a class="accent-color text-decoration-none" href="mailto:hello@<%= Rails.application.secrets.host %>">hello@<%= Rails.application.secrets.host %>↳</a>.
            </p>
            <p class='faq-text h5'>
              We’re run by a team of volunteers, and all of our administrative costs are supported by private philanthropy which enables us to ensure every dollar raised goes directly to supporting the causes you care about most. Interested in supporting the platform? You can reach us at <a class="accent-color text-decoration-none" href="mailto:hello@<%= Rails.application.secrets.host %>">hello@<%= Rails.application.secrets.host %>↳</a>. We’d love to continue the conversation!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='faq-text-box'>
            <p class='faq-subheading sofiabold dgray h4'>Liability & responsibility</p>
            <p class='faq-text h5'>
              Our goal is to connect willing and able volunteers directly with credible community organizations.
            </p>
            <p class='faq-text h5'>
              <%= Rails.application.secrets.name %> is not liable for any personal damages, injury, or lost property during participant’s activation. Before an activation, each volunteer is required to fill out a waiver.
            </p>
            <p class='faq-text h5'>
              While we help coordinate the activations, you’ll be dealing directly with the organizations who may have their own requirements and paperwork for you to fill out.
            </p>
            <p class='faq-text h5'>
              If you have any specific questions, email us at <a class="accent-color text-decoration-none" href="mailto:hello@give-one.org">hello@give-one.org↳</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='faq-text-box'>
            <p class='faq-subheading sofiabold dgray h4'>We're in beta</p>
            <p class='faq-text h5'>
              We are currently Beta testing our volunteer activations with select partners in New York City.
            </p>
            <p class='faq-text h5'>
              We will be expanding our programming to additional communities and community organizers in the months to come. If you have an organization that would like to participate, or would like to suggest an organization, please email us at <a class="accent-color text-decoration-none" href="mailto:partners@give-one.org">partners@give-one.org↳</a>.
            </p>
            <p class='faq-text accent-color h5'>
              We’d love to help!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
